cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper presents a novel approach for image segmentation and free space perception using active contours. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) domains. The paper also involves curve evolution and modeling, which could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the approach involves adapting to various shape settings and handling topology changes, which could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
